  "detailed_description": "HAELE 3D - Feet Poses Lite is an easy to use anatomy drawing reference tool designed for beginner to advanced artists. It serves as a resource for learning how to draw human feet. Whether your art style is realistic, stylized, cartoon, anime or anything in between this is easy to use app complements tutorials and aids practicing your foot drawing or sculpting skills from sketch to finish.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2378840/extras/9b7050fe8e160dbbcb2ae3d6501c7b5b.poster.avif?t=1773168386\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2378840/extras/9b7050fe8e160dbbcb2ae3d6501c7b5b.webm?t=1773168386\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2378840/extras/9b7050fe8e160dbbcb2ae3d6501c7b5b.mp4?t=1773168386\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2378840/extras/a7c61348b895548e2aa9bad78bf6d2ce.poster.avif?t=1773168386\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2378840/extras/a7c61348b895548e2aa9bad78bf6d2ce.webm?t=1773168386\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2378840/extras/a7c61348b895548e2aa9bad78bf6d2ce.mp4?t=1773168386\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2378840/extras/5f73775d4552f2ca7d10260ddc2c6827.poster.avif?t=1773168386\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2378840/extras/5f73775d4552f2ca7d10260ddc2c6827.webm?t=1773168386\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2378840/extras/5f73775d4552f2ca7d10260ddc2c6827.mp4?t=1773168386\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2378840/extras/c4746c12116908a162b1ea453a6b219a.poster.avif?t=1773168386\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2378840/extras/c4746c12116908a162b1ea453a6b219a.webm?t=1773168386\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2378840/extras/c4746c12116908a162b1ea453a6b219a.mp4?t=1773168386\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Features:</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Preset poses<br></li><li>Custom posing<br></li><li>Editable lights: Point light (color, intensity transformation), Environment light (HDRI map, intensity), Ground light (color, intensity) <br></li><li>Environment: HDRI studio backgrounds, Solid colors, <br></li><li>Floor on/off, color, reflectivity<br></li><li>Skin material: editable details, reflectivity, tone saturation, variation<br></li><li>Colors: preset skin colors, grayscale and skin tones,<br></li><li>Nails: shine, tone<br></li><li>Adjustable camera angle, location, position and field of view<br></li><li>Save and load scenes<br></li><li>Load presets</li></ul>",
  "about_the_game": "HAELE 3D - Feet Poses Lite is an easy to use anatomy drawing reference tool designed for beginner to advanced artists. It serves as a resource for learning how to draw human feet. Whether your art style is realistic, stylized, cartoon, anime or anything in between this is easy to use app complements tutorials and aids practicing your foot drawing or sculpting skills from sketch to finish.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2378840/extras/9b7050fe8e160dbbcb2ae3d6501c7b5b.poster.avif?t=1773168386\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2378840/extras/9b7050fe8e160dbbcb2ae3d6501c7b5b.webm?t=1773168386\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2378840/extras/9b7050fe8e160dbbcb2ae3d6501c7b5b.mp4?t=1773168386\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2378840/extras/a7c61348b895548e2aa9bad78bf6d2ce.poster.avif?t=1773168386\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2378840/extras/a7c61348b895548e2aa9bad78bf6d2ce.webm?t=1773168386\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2378840/extras/a7c61348b895548e2aa9bad78bf6d2ce.mp4?t=1773168386\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2378840/extras/5f73775d4552f2ca7d10260ddc2c6827.poster.avif?t=1773168386\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/